WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:05.066
A useful sample starts with a clear question and a readable journal.

2
00:00:07.339 --> 00:00:14.151
Vera imports the file, identifies dates, accounts, descriptions, debits and credits,

3
00:00:14.151 --> 00:00:17.800
and makes the period and population explicit.

4
00:00:20.074 --> 00:00:26.155
It then applies the selected approach: value coverage, unusual entries, intervals,

5
00:00:26.155 --> 00:00:30.308
targeted selection or a combination suited to the check.

6
00:00:32.581 --> 00:00:37.345
Every selected row retains its population reference and selection reason.

7
00:00:39.619 --> 00:00:45.280
The firm receives the sample, normalized population and a concise method summary,

8
00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:48.146
so the step can be repeated and reviewed.

9
00:00:50.420 --> 00:00:54.200
From the full journal to the entries that deserve focused checking.
